When a Wi-Fi connection is available

Send a diagnostics report when the device experiences a software error. This might incur additional charges depending on your network and data plan. It is recommended that you check your data allowance before proceeding.

You are about to stop participating in our User Experience Program. Software errors that occur on your phone won’t be kept and sent, and so we won’t be able to study them to improve your experience while using the phone.
